              <span class="pre">Next Event</span>
              <h3>Tues, Oct 7</h3>
              <h4 class="time">7 – 9pm</h4>
              <h4 class="loc">Samovar Tea Lounge Hayes Valley, 297 Page Street</h4>
              <h4 class="cost">$25</h4>
              <a class="button" target="_blank" href="https://www.tilt.com/campaigns/stranger-open-house-iii?utm_source=TWS&utm_medium=landing&utm_campaign=ohIII">Get a ticket!</a>
