            <div class="box-section general-info">
              <span class="pre">The General Lowdown</span>
              <h2>
                Open House is an experiment. Each one is different.
              </h2>
              <h4>
                We're learning how to design an evening for large numbers and amazing conversations.
              </h4>
              <p>
                We're going to be trying new things while we work to find something that we know will be awesome, every time. (Well, a significant portion of the time. No such thing as perfect.)
